Salt Shaker Body: A sphere or curved cylinder
Parameters: body_height=100, body_bottom_radius=30, body_mid_radius=50, body_top_radius=30
Orientation: body_origin=(0,0,0), body_normal=ZAxis

Salt Shaker Base Rim: A flat surface in a circle shape at the bottom of the salt shaker.
Parameters: base_rim_radius=body_bottom_radius
Orientation: base_origin=body_origin, base_normal=body_normal

Salt Shaker Top: A perforated flat disk or a hemisphere shape. The holes are located in few circles around the center of the surface
Parameters: lid_radius=body_radius, holes_radius=0.5,  holes_amount=10, holes_distance_from_center=15, holes_circles_amount=2
Orientation: lid_origin=(0,0,body_height), lid_normal=body_normal